metadata.name: Mother of Pearl
metadata.description:
Iridescent and translucent, an intricate array of multicoloured forms glows before you.  Nestled around a core that your eyes can't penetrate,  energy emanates from within.  

What is this?   What is it made of?  Where are we?  When are we?

This, Mother of Pearl, is timeless, and the realm of creation and infinite potential - the source of manifestation, the unmanifest.  

Imagination draws from its infinite supply, breathing life into the wildest of creations...what will come from yours?
